      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison at 2.5 L/min 2400 RPM",
      "description": "Computational velocity magnitudes compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements in the pump volute at the nominal CPB operating point. Mean absolute error across 847 measurement locations was 4.2% of peak velocity. Aleatory uncertainty arising from inter-run PIV scatter and pump assembly variability is acknowledged in the discussion section but is not formally propagated through a UQ artifact.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/uq-01-piv-velocity-aleatory"
