      "name": "Pump pressure rise validation across 5 operating points",
      "description": "Predicted total-to-total pressure rise compared against bench measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations (2.0–4.5 L/min, 2000–3000 RPM). Maximum relative error 6.8%; mean 3.1%. Experimental uncertainty from transducer calibration (±0.5 mmHg) and flow meter accuracy (±1.5%) is noted qualitatively in the text.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/uq-02-pressure-rise-combined"
    },
    {
