      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution comparison at impeller blade surfaces",
      "description": "CFD-predicted wall shear stress (WSS) on impeller blade pressure and suction surfaces compared against high-resolution PIV-derived WSS estimates at 2.5 L/min. Spatial correlation coefficient R = 0.91. The authors note that stochastic turbulence fluctuations and measurement noise introduce aleatory uncertainty in both the experimental WSS derivation and the instantaneous CFD snapshots; this is discussed qualitatively without attachment of a formal UQ node."
    },
