      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/vr-05-grid-convergence",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Grid convergence index assessment for hemolysis-sensitive regions",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation and GCI analysis performed on three systematically refined meshes (3.2 M, 8.7 M, 18.4 M cells). GCI for NIH prediction 2.3% on fine mesh. Discretisation uncertainty formally bounded.",
