      "description": "NIH predictions compared between two turbulence closures to bound model-form uncertainty. Difference in predicted RH < 0.04 across all operating points, confirming low sensitivity. Aleatory variation in inlet turbulence intensity (measured range 3–8%) propagated through both models is referenced in the text but the corresponding UQ artifact is not linked to this validation result entry."
